lyrics:
[Verse]
All my life I was second in line
Never the first, just left behind
Watching others shine in the spotlight
But now it's time to make things right

[Chorus]
No more playing second fiddle, I'll rise
Gonna break the cycle, reach for the skies
With the funk in my soul, gonna rock this show
It's my time to shine, watch me glow
style: Red Hot Chili Pepper funk rock
